  "solution": {
    "outline": [],
    "steps": [
      { "idx": 1, "description": "先化简差：用 sin^3+cos^3=(sin+cos)(1-sin cos)。", "math": "f-g=3(\\sin x+\\cos x)-a(\\sin^3x+\\cos^3x)=(\\sin x+\\cos x)\\left(3-a+\\frac{a}{2}\\sin2x\\right)" },
      { "idx": 2, "description": "(1) 令括号为0：sin2x=2(a-3)/a，并用 2x∈[0,4π/3] 的取值范围判断 a。", "math": "\\sin2x\\in\\left[-\\frac{\\sqrt3}{2},1\\right]\\Rightarrow 3\\le a\\le 6" },
      { "idx": 3, "description": "(2) 取 a=4，求导并找临界点。", "math": "f'(x)=-3\\sin x(1+2\\sin2x),\\ g'(x)=-3\\cos x(1+2\\sin2x)" },
      { "idx": 4, "description": "求交点：f-g=0 ⇒ -1+2 sin2x=0 ⇒ x=π/12,5π/12。", "math": "" },
      { "idx": 5, "description": "面积：S=∫_{π/12}^{5π/12}(f-g)dx，并化为三倍角余弦积分。", "math": "f-g=(\\sin x+\\cos x)(-1+2\\sin2x)=-\\sqrt2\\cos(3x+\\pi/4)\\Rightarrow S=\\frac{2\\sqrt2}{3}" }
    ],
